### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Envoyer invitations à tous les invités (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Envoyer invitations à des invités spécifiques
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "guest_ids": ["guest-uuid-1", "guest-uuid-2"]
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: event_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: aucun invité trouvé
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-without-guests-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: invités sans contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/guests/send-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-with-guests-no-contact-uuid"
}

